An arched black iron gate barely taller than you. It looks like this kind lifts upward by a hidden pulley or chain.
You try to lift the bars, but they are much too heavy.
...Do you intend to pick the lock with that? Well, perhaps you could, but then again, you are not learned of this skill. Yet another you yearn for at the moment.
You aren't sure what you'd search for on a gate.